{"tid":2125012,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英報：美斯希望巴塞請比爾沙執教","createTime":"2020-07-26T01:15:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T15:15:42.000Z","uid":173952,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"bb6f608051c90a05c03b6c4ba8d25ba2ce3d65f2","tid":2125012,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T01:15:50.000Z","msg":"據英國媒體報導，美斯（Lionel Messi）希望巴塞隆拿聘請比爾沙（Marcelo Bielsa）成為新教練。<br />\n<br />\n  《太陽報》稱，美斯告知巴塞，希望請比爾沙來執教。該報稱，美斯認為這位阿根廷教練是接替巴塞帥位的理想人選。<br />\n<br />\n  在帶隊衝上英超後，比爾沙尚未與列斯聯達成續約協議，他和該球會的合約本週就要到期，目前列斯聯正在努力試圖與他達成續約。"},{"pid":"5dd12f1bb6339ada80465bd9b1df16735e0dcb7e","tid":2125012,"uid":3028,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T01:25:20.000Z","msg":"你過黎列斯好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dc05cd6a104ecdc0e43decf1b7fb98df7c375ed","tid":2125012,"uid":18395,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T01:27:07.000Z","msg":"比爾沙應該一個禮拜辭職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d9f0a0552f5efa11929cb1d779f52d991aa39bd","tid":2125012,"uid":234945,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T01:51:33.000Z","msg":"含血噴人，美斯根本唔會搞呢啲小動作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c76a9f253e5562e734a724ea157a922dd2f00765","tid":2125012,"uid":60524,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T02:37:35.000Z","msg":"比爾沙過黎比美斯教呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c4d4dbdf848f0060876c5b380f7303e6ddb5c8","tid":2125012,"uid":261873,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T02:48:25.000Z","msg":"自己唔敢去<br />\n就阻住人地去挑戰英超"},{"pid":"eee15ba7268b6f0de1aa80abcc448ea7d384a99f","tid":2125012,"uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c76a9f253e5562e734a724ea157a922dd2f00765","tid":2125012,"uid":60524,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"